/docs/DAGOR_PARITY.md
/ROADMAP-old.md
**/*DAGOR*.md
**/*Dagor*.md
**/*CRYENGINE*.md
**/*CryEngine*.md

# Proprietary / large SDKs in 3thirdy (keep READMEs + scripts)
/3thirdy/nsight-aftermath/**
!/3thirdy/nsight-aftermath/README.md
!/3thirdy/nsight-aftermath/.gitkeep
/3thirdy/nsight-aftermath-samples/
/3thirdy/_incoming/
/3thirdy/**/*.lib
/3thirdy/**/*.dll
/3thirdy/**/*.pdb
/3thirdy/**/*.exe


# Large / regenerable content
/Assets/Sponza/
/Assets/_gltf_tmp/
/Assets/sponza.zip
*.tif
*.TIF

# Runtime caches
/cache/dx12_pso.cache
*.cache

/captures/*.txt
/captures/*.dot

# Local vcpkg clone
/Tools/vcpkg/

# TestPlay deploy (keep README; ignore built binaries / shaders)
/TestPlay/*.exe
/TestPlay/*.dll
/TestPlay/*.pdb
/TestPlay/shaders/
/TestPlay/*.png
!/TestPlay/README.md
!/TestPlay/.gitkeep

